{"tid":2417154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［沈旭暉/WS Post] 中國強制要求美國外交官 做了屎眼武漢肺炎測試","createTime":"2021-02-21T15:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T05:27:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a7a65f4bbc15efcf253700bad6788263a81339","tid":2417154,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"《華盛頓郵報》報導，不少美國駐華外交官投訴，被中國當局強制要求進行全球只有中國獨家的「肛門檢測」檢疫。這完全是超乎任何常理想像。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯根據關於外交官規範的《維也納公約》，中國有沒有權力作出如此要求，實屬疑問，儘管中國也有權訂立規定：拒絕遵從中國當局檢疫要求的，將不得入境。然而是否所有外交官都要「通櫃」，還是特別保障美國「友人」之舉，同樣語焉不詳。<br />\n<br />\n這動作一來傳遞政治、醫學訊息：中國不信任美國的檢測，而中國疫情比美國控制得好，所以中國的專業建議自然應該遵從，「誰叫你們不爭氣」？<br />\n<br />\n但此外，更有深層象徵意義。正如《華盛頓郵報》報導，美國國務院發言人要求保障「外交官尊嚴」，明顯認為「通櫃檢測」損害人性尊嚴，將當事人當作囚犯、動物，何況其科學根據成疑，更有合理理由拒絕⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/state-department-coronavirus-vaccine-diplomats/2021/02/17/ec507e84-70d5-11eb-a4eb-44012a612cf9_story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2Fstate-department-coronavirus-vaccine-diplomats%2F2021%2F02%2F17%2Fec507e84-70d5-11eb-a4eb-44012a612cf9_story.html&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=02ee435d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/state-department-coronavirus-vaccine-diplomats/2021/02/17/ec507e84-70d5-11eb-a4eb-44012a612cf9_story.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/47812769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F47812769&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=ce9ef1cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/47812769</a>"},{"pid":"f7a531f4a1386de1596fe3122838a219aa6a7786","tid":2417154,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets